{"title":"Sigma Sports’ best Black Friday deals on bikes and tech in 2024","link":"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/sponsored/sigma-sports-black-friday-deals-2024","date":1732545668000,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk\">Cyclist</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/sponsored/sigma-sports-black-friday-deals-2024\">Sigma Sports’ best Black Friday deals on bikes and tech in 2024</a></p>\n\n<p>The UK’s foremost retailer of premium bikes, tech and clothing, Sigma Sports, has a whole host of great deals across its range this Black Friday.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With big discounts on products including high-end bikes, computers, clothing for winter and summer, helmets, turbo trainers, shoes, wheels and more, it’s the perfect opportunity to stock up on things you both want and need, whether it’s for you or for a big ticket Christmas present. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here is a selection of Sigma Sports’ best Black Friday cycling deals.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Specialized Tarmac SL7 Comp 105 Di2 – save 34%</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"748\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Specialized-Tarmac-SL7-Comp-105-Di2-Road-Bike-2024-Satin-Obsidian-Smoke-970x748.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Specialized-Tarmac-SL7-Comp-105-Di2-Road-Bike-2024-Satin-Obsidian-Smoke-970x748.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Specialized-Tarmac-SL7-Comp-105-Di2-Road-Bike-2024-Satin-Obsidian-Smoke-300x231.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Specialized-Tarmac-SL7-Comp-105-Di2-Road-Bike-2024-Satin-Obsidian-Smoke-768x592.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Specialized-Tarmac-SL7-Comp-105-Di2-Road-Bike-2024-Satin-Obsidian-Smoke-750x579.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Specialized-Tarmac-SL7-Comp-105-Di2-Road-Bike-2024-Satin-Obsidian-Smoke-1140x879.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Specialized-Tarmac-SL7-Comp-105-Di2-Road-Bike-2024-Satin-Obsidian-Smoke.jpg 1400w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h4>Was £4,250, now £2,799 | <a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=25809&amp;awinaffid=1306327&amp;clickref=tarmac+bf&amp;ued=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sigmasports.com%2Fitem%2FSpecialized%2FTarmac-SL7-Comp-105-Di2-Road-Bike-2024%2F11HZM%3Fs%3D1\" target=\"_blank\">View offer</a></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the best value road bikes on the market is even better value this Black Friday with Sigma Sports. This Specialized Tarmac SL7 has electronic shifting, hydraulic disc brakes, DT Swiss R470 wheels, 26mm Specialized Turbo Pro tyres and more. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Plus it looks great and a size 56 weighs 8.1kg.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=25809&amp;awinaffid=1306327&amp;clickref=tarmac+bf&amp;ued=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sigmasports.com%2Fitem%2FSpecialized%2FTarmac-SL7-Comp-105-Di2-Road-Bike-2024%2F11HZM%3Fs%3D1\" target=\"_blank\">Buy it now from Sigma Sports</a></strong></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Cervélo S5 Ultegra Di2 – save up to 35%</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"952\" height=\"943\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Cervelo-Sigma.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Cervelo-Sigma.jpg 952w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Cervelo-Sigma-300x297.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Cervelo-Sigma-150x150.jpg 150w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Cervelo-Sigma-768x761.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Cervelo-Sigma-75x75.jpg 75w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Cervelo-Sigma-750x743.jpg 750w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h4>Was £9,200, now £5,999 | <a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=25809&amp;awinaffid=1306327&amp;ued=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sigmasports.com%2Fitem%2FCervelo%2FS5-Ultegra-Di2-Disc-Road-Bike%2FZAIN\" target=\"_blank\">View offer</a></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>For those looking for bargains on aero, how about this Cervélo S5? As seen winning all sorts of races under Wout van Aert and co, it’s proven on the biggest stage. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>This model comes with Shimano’s second-tier 12-speed Ultegra Di2 groupset with Reserve 63/52mm aero carbon wheels, which are tubeless-ready and come fitted with 28mm Vittoria Corsa TLR G tyres.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=25809&amp;awinaffid=1306327&amp;ued=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sigmasports.com%2Fitem%2FCervelo%2FS5-Ultegra-Di2-Disc-Road-Bike%2FZAIN\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Buy it now from Sigma Sports</strong></a></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Cannondale Synapse Carbon 4 – save up to 40%</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"951\" height=\"777\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Cannondale-Sigma.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Cannondale-Sigma.jpg 951w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Cannondale-Sigma-300x245.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Cannondale-Sigma-768x627.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Cannondale-Sigma-750x613.jpg 750w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h4>Was £2,400, now £1,449 | <a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=25809&amp;awinaffid=1306327&amp;clickref=synapse+bf&amp;ued=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sigmasports.com%2Fitem%2FCannondale%2FSynapse-Carbon-4-Disc-Road-Bike-2024%2FX3IH%3Fs%3D1\" target=\"_blank\">View offer</a></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>For those looking for a more comfortable ride, this Cannondale Synapse could be the one for you. The Synapse was the original endurance road bike, with a geometry that keeps the rider comfortable for as many kilometres as required. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The carbon fibre frame with light aero touches is paired with a 10-speed Shimano Tiagra groupset, Cannondale RD3.1 wheels with 30mm Vittoria Zaffiro Pro Reflective tyres – although the frame has clearance for 35mm.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=25809&amp;awinaffid=1306327&amp;clickref=synapse+bf&amp;ued=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sigmasports.com%2Fitem%2FCannondale%2FSynapse-Carbon-4-Disc-Road-Bike-2024%2FX3IH%3Fs%3D1\" target=\"_blank\">Buy it now from Sigma Sports</a></strong></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Rapha Core Short Sleeve Jersey – save 37%</h2>\n\n\n<div>\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"970\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Rapha-Core-Short-Sleeve-Jersey-Navy-Mix-970x970.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Rapha-Core-Short-Sleeve-Jersey-Navy-Mix-970x970.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Rapha-Core-Short-Sleeve-Jersey-Navy-Mix-300x300.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Rapha-Core-Short-Sleeve-Jersey-Navy-Mix-150x150.jpg 150w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Rapha-Core-Short-Sleeve-Jersey-Navy-Mix-768x768.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Rapha-Core-Short-Sleeve-Jersey-Navy-Mix-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Rapha-Core-Short-Sleeve-Jersey-Navy-Mix-75x75.jpg 75w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Rapha-Core-Short-Sleeve-Jersey-Navy-Mix-350x350.jpg 350w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Rapha-Core-Short-Sleeve-Jersey-Navy-Mix-750x750.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Rapha-Core-Short-Sleeve-Jersey-Navy-Mix-1140x1140.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Rapha-Core-Short-Sleeve-Jersey-Navy-Mix.jpg 2000w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n<h4>Was £78, now £49 | <a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=25809&amp;awinaffid=1306327&amp;ued=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sigmasports.com%2Fitem%2FRapha%2FCore-Short-Sleeve-Jersey%2F110WL%3Fs%3D1\" target=\"_blank\">View offer</a></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Arguably <em>the </em>cycling jersey of the last 15 years, you’ve either had a Rapha Core short sleeve jersey or you know someone who has. Now Sigma has it discounted to below £50, ideal if you’re after a quality jersey for a fraction of the price of most options.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>It could also be the ideal gift for someone looking to get more into cycling this Christmas.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=25809&amp;awinaffid=1306327&amp;ued=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sigmasports.com%2Fitem%2FRapha%2FCore-Short-Sleeve-Jersey%2F110WL%3Fs%3D1\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Buy it now from Sigma Sports</strong></a></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Kask Mojito3 WG11 helmet – save up to 50%</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"745\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Kask-helmet-Sigma-970x745.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Kask-helmet-Sigma-970x745.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Kask-helmet-Sigma-300x231.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Kask-helmet-Sigma-768x590.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Kask-helmet-Sigma-750x576.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Kask-helmet-Sigma.jpg 1088w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h4>Was £139, now £69.99 | <a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=25809&amp;awinaffid=1306327&amp;clickref=kask+bf&amp;ued=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sigmasports.com%2Fitem%2FKask%2FMojito3-WG11-Road-Helmet%2FV2AA%3Fs%3D1\" target=\"_blank\">View offer</a></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Sigma also has deals on helmets this Black Friday, including Kask’s Mojito3, another classic of its genre.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>It’s built with Kask’s WG11 safety technology, along with Blue Tech sweat-wicking and anti-bacterial padding and an eco-leather section on the strap for extra comfort. Kask says a size medium weighs just 230g.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=25809&amp;awinaffid=1306327&amp;clickref=kask+bf&amp;ued=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sigmasports.com%2Fitem%2FKask%2FMojito3-WG11-Road-Helmet%2FV2AA%3Fs%3D1\" target=\"_blank\">Buy it now from Sigma Sports</a></strong></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Universal Colours Mono Bib Tight – save up to 53%</h2>\n\n\n<div>\n<figure><img width=\"479\" height=\"801\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Universal-Colours-Bib-Sigma.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Universal-Colours-Bib-Sigma.jpg 479w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Universal-Colours-Bib-Sigma-179x300.jpg 179w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n<h4>Was £160, now £70 | <a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=25809&amp;awinaffid=1306327&amp;ued=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sigmasports.com%2Fitem%2FUniversal-Colours%2FMono-Bib-Tight%2FUPKE%3Fs%3D1+\" target=\"_blank\">View offer</a></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Just in time for winter, Universal Colours’ Mono bib tights are available for as little as £70. They’re made with recycled materials in a Bluesign-approved factory, meaning they’re not only ideal for keeping the cold out, but they’re also an environmentally conscious choice.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>They’re built from Italian nylon fabric with a PFC-free water-repellent treatment and an Elastic Interface pad, and mesh straps that attach higher up the body for improved insulation around your core.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=25809&amp;awinaffid=1306327&amp;ued=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sigmasports.com%2Fitem%2FUniversal-Colours%2FMono-Bib-Tight%2FUPKE%3Fs%3D1+\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Buy it now from Sigma Sports</strong></a></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Castelli Salto Infinium Jacket – save 55%</h2>\n\n\n<div>\n<figure><img width=\"946\" height=\"949\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Castelli-Sigma.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Castelli-Sigma.jpg 946w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Castelli-Sigma-300x300.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Castelli-Sigma-150x150.jpg 150w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Castelli-Sigma-768x770.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Castelli-Sigma-75x75.jpg 75w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Castelli-Sigma-350x350.jpg 350w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Castelli-Sigma-750x752.jpg 750w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n<h4>Was £199, now £89 | <a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=25809&amp;awinaffid=1306327&amp;ued=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sigmasports.com%2Fitem%2FCastelli%2FSalto-Infinium-Jacket%2F13P5U\" target=\"_blank\">View offer</a></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Castelli’s Salto Infinium jacket is a windproof outer layer made with Gore-Tex Infinium Windstopper 150 fabric that helps keep you warm without needing chunky layers. It’s finished with DWR treatment to repel water from the road or the sky and it’s built like a jersey with a racy but stretchy fit and three back pockets.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=25809&amp;awinaffid=1306327&amp;ued=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sigmasports.com%2Fitem%2FCastelli%2FSalto-Infinium-Jacket%2F13P5U\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Buy it now from Sigma Sports</strong></a></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Garmin Edge 1040 GPS computer – save 23%</h2>\n\n\n<div>\n<figure><img width=\"790\" height=\"791\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Garmin-Sigma.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Garmin-Sigma.jpg 790w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Garmin-Sigma-300x300.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Garmin-Sigma-150x150.jpg 150w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Garmin-Sigma-768x769.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Garmin-Sigma-75x75.jpg 75w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Garmin-Sigma-350x350.jpg 350w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Garmin-Sigma-750x751.jpg 750w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n<h4>Was £519.99, now £399.99 | <a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=25809&amp;awinaffid=1306327&amp;ued=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sigmasports.com%2Fitem%2FGarmin%2FEdge-1040-GPS-Cycling-Computer%2FY6HN\" target=\"_blank\">View offer</a></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>It’s hard to find a computer as good as this, so this is a great time to pick up a deal. Garmin’s 1040 offers all the data and navigation you need and even more, including stamina insights, workout recommendations, the ClimbPro feature, and mountain bike data including Flow, which measures how smoothly you descend a trail.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Its battery lasts up to 70 hours in battery-saver mode and 35 hours in the most intense use cases.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=25809&amp;awinaffid=1306327&amp;ued=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sigmasports.com%2Fitem%2FGarmin%2FEdge-1040-GPS-Cycling-Computer%2FY6HN\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Buy it now from Sigma Sports</strong></a></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Tacx Flux S smart turbo trainer – save 33%</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"799\" height=\"764\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Tacx-Sigma.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Tacx-Sigma.jpg 799w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Tacx-Sigma-300x287.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Tacx-Sigma-768x734.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/Tacx-Sigma-750x717.jpg 750w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h4>Was £599.99, now £399 | <a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=25809&amp;awinaffid=1306327&amp;ued=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sigmasports.com%2Fitem%2FTacx%2FFLUX-S-Smart-Turbo-Trainer-T2900S%2FK104\" target=\"_blank\">View offer</a></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>It’s indoor season. Even the hardiest of riders can’t go outside every day, so finding a bargain on a smart turbo trainer should be on everyone’s radar. The Flux S from Tacx has all the connectivity you’re after, with power readings for speed, cadence and power provided to 3% accuracy.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>It’s compatible with road, MTB and time-trial bikes with 8-11 speed cassettes, has a max incline of 10%, max power of 1,500 watts and has one of the quietest flywheels on the market.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=25809&amp;awinaffid=1306327&amp;ued=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sigmasports.com%2Fitem%2FTacx%2FFLUX-S-Smart-Turbo-Trainer-T2900S%2FK104\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Buy it now from Sigma Sports</strong></a></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Specialized S-Works Torch road cycling shoes – save up to 55%</h2>\n\n\n<div>\n<figure><img width=\"801\" height=\"791\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/S-Works-shoes-Sigma.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/S-Works-shoes-Sigma.jpg 801w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/S-Works-shoes-Sigma-300x296.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/S-Works-shoes-Sigma-768x758.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/S-Works-shoes-Sigma-75x75.jpg 75w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/11/S-Works-shoes-Sigma-750x741.jpg 750w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n<h4>Was £350, now £157 | <a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=25809&amp;awinaffid=1306327&amp;clickref=torch+bf&amp;ued=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sigmasports.com%2Fitem%2FSpecialized%2FS-Works-Torch-Road-Cycling-Shoes%2FY9XR%3Fs%3D1\" target=\"_blank\">View offer</a></h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Cycling shoes don’t get much better than this, Specialized’s latest and greatest road racing shoes, the S-Works Torch. They’re made with Specialized’s Body Geometry, comfort-enhancing and pain-reducing features, with a stiff carbon sole that’s 20g lighter than its predecessor and two Boa S3 dials for a balanced closure system and easy adjustment.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The upper has reinforced areas with a low collar made possible thanks to the asymmetric heel counter providing enough support lower down, and the new last is designed using Specialized’s Retül bike fitting data, so it’s based on real riders’ feet and has a snug, close-to-foot fit.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.awin1.com/cread.php?awinmid=25809&amp;awinaffid=1306327&amp;clickref=torch+bf&amp;ued=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sigmasports.com%2Fitem%2FSpecialized%2FS-Works-Torch-Road-Cycling-Shoes%2FY9XR%3Fs%3D1\" target=\"_blank\">Buy it now from Sigma Sports</a></strong></l